%h1 Welcome to the HOAP Admin Interface

%p
  <b>Status</b>:
  = pluralize @count, "participant has", "participants have"
  done the survey.

%p
  <b>Available Participant Codes</b>

%ul
  - @available.each do |key|
    %li= link_to key, start_link_url(key)

= form_tag :action => :participant do
  %p
    Make
    = select_tag :count, options_for_select((1..10).to_a)
    new participant codes
    = submit_tag "Go!"
